maintainers         {@barracuda156 macos-powerpc.org:barracuda} openmaintainer
description         Delightful Ruby way to work with AI
long_description    {*}${description}
homepage            https://rubyllm.com
checksums           rmd160  12b4dc41638d2624bb7fda097cf15613e66bcc56 \
                    sha256  5f3972e2aab41c64791fd83492f0c85fb449efc9574c3c8d8fdfb2d009f46f90 \
